data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET. Charming 3 bedroom, 2 and half bath, light and bright! Formal living and dining plus a den.  First floor with ceramic tile, hardwood floors upstairs, granite counter top.  Walking distance to the tennis court, club house and pool.  Community has 3 swimming pools, 2 tennis courts play grounds, quiet green area in front. Carport and storage area.  EXCELLENT SCHOOLS. NEVER FLOODED!
